title: Five Hours from Paris - Hamesh shaot me'Pariz [2009 - Israel]
description: Five Hours from Paris [2009 - Israel] Hamesh shaot me'Pariz חמש שעות מפריז Drama http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1345469/ Only five flight hours from Paris, in a working-class suburb of Tel Aviv, two people meet. Yigal is a taxi driver with a burning desire to visit Paris. His fear of flying stands in the way of him booking a flight from Tel Aviv. He forms a deep emotional bond with a married Russian emigrant, Lina, who plans to immigrate to Canada. Winner of Best Film at both the Haifa and Napoli International Film Festivals.
